      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; scoped out per V&V 40 Table 3.",
      "rationale": "Formal model input uncertainty quantification is not required at Model Risk Level 2. Nominal values for fluid viscosity, density, and damage model coefficients were taken from published literature. Sensitivity to ±10% variation in key inputs was informally checked and found to produce less than 5% change in RH rankings."
