    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at Model Risk Level 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 for the declared combination of medium model influence and high decision consequence. The CFD model is judged to have adequate credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 acceptance criterion is met at the worst-case operating point identified by the model.",
